erson\u2019s nonverbal communication, such as facial expressions, tone of voice, and body language. Nonverbal communication can help you understand the other person\u2019s emotions and intentions."),mdx("h2",null,"It Helps Build Relationships"),mdx("p",null,`The process of mediation helps you and the other person in the dispute understand each other\u2019s situation and come to a reasonable resolution. It can also help you establish a more positive relationship with the other person by showing that you are willing to compromise and come to an agreement.
